OL,3,CResidents concerned about council
OL,4,Cproposals to close public toilets
OL,6,FHe said: " As a retired GP from a
OL,7,Fpublic health point of view, where are
OL,8,Fpeople going to go to use the toilets
OL,9,Fif we haven't got a public
OL,10,Fconvenience."
OL,12,FAge Cymru say according to their
OL,13,Flatest annual survey the lack of safe,
OL,14,Faccessible, and well-maintained public
OL,15,Ftoilets makes it difficult for many
OL,16,Folder people to get out into their
OL,17,Fcommunities.
