OL,3,CResidents concerned about council
OL,4,Cproposals to close public toilets
OL,6,FThey stated: "The lack of suitable
OL,7,Fpublic toilets means many older people
OL,8,Fare worried about not being able to
OL,9,Faccess facilities when needed and so
OL,10,Fstruggle to leave their homes, making
OL,11,Fthem increasingly lonely and isolated.
OL,13,F"For others, we've heard of cases
OL,14,Fwhere older people will deliberately
OL,15,Fde-hydrate themselves to reduce their
OL,16,Fneed to visit a toilet.
