OL,3,CResidents concerned about council
OL,4,Cproposals to close public toilets
OL,6,F"We have had to deliver #10.4m of
OL,7,Fsavings as part of the 2024/25 budget,
OL,8,Fand the proposal to review the public
OL,9,Fconvenience provision in the County is
OL,10,Fone of the savings proposals
OL,11,Fidentified."
OL,13,FThey say while there is no legal
OL,14,Frequirement for them to provide public
OL,15,Ftoilets, they do need to evidence that
OL,16,Fthey have reviewed the needs of the
OL,17,Flocal population and to produce a
OL,18,Fstrategy that shows how it will try to
OL,19,Fmeet these needs.
