OL,3,CResidents concerned about council
OL,4,Cproposals to close public toilets
OL,6,F"As a result, the Council is currently
OL,7,Fcarrying out a needs assessment for
OL,8,Fthe public conveniences in the County.
OL,9,FThis will identify the number of
OL,10,Fpublic conveniences needed in
OL,11,FDenbighshire and will help the Council
OL,12,Fto develop a suitable Public Toilet
OL,13,FStrategy.
OL,15,F"To develop this Strategy, a public
OL,16,Fconsultation is currently underway and
OL,17,Fresidents, business owners and
OL,18,Fvisitors have been encouraged to take
OL,19,Fpart and have their say.
