OL,3,CResidents concerned about council
OL,4,Cproposals to close public toilets
OL,6,F"In areas where the provision of
OL,7,Fpublic conveniences is considered
OL,8,Fessential, The Council hopes to work
OL,9,Fwith City, Town and Community Councils
OL,10,Fto look at alternative arrangements.
OL,12,F"We are also promoting interest in the
OL,13,FCommunity Toilet Grant Scheme whereby
OL,14,Fbusinesses can apply to join the
OL,15,Fscheme, which allows the pubic to use
OL,16,Ftoilet facilities during their opening
OL,17,Fhours without any expectation that
OL,18,Fusers will make a purchase or use
OL,19,Ftheir services.
